item.title: SoftLayer_Notification_User_Subscriber_Mobile
item.description: SoftLayer_Notification_User_Subscriber_Mobile Service Datatype Description A notification subscriber will have details pertaining to the subscriber’s notification subscription. You can receive details such as preferences, details of the preferences, delivery methods and the delivery methods for the subscriber. NOTE: There are preferences and delivery methods that cannot be modified. Also, there are some subscriptions that are required. Local active The current status of the subscription. Type: integer
